summary: I\'ve tried many different ENB presets, most of them I don\'t like. So here\'s my ENB settings that I currently use. Nights are fairly dark, days are still bright, but more contrast and definition to really bring out textures. These settings are for a more realistic feel to the game.
descriptionHtml:
Installation:

First download and install ENB Enhanced shaders here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=822

Next download my preset and paste both enbeffect and enbseries into the main skyrim folder. When asked to overwrite/replace, do so.

That\'s it.

Cheers!
author: Satch500
